request.description: Collected by has a max 50 characters length
No collection date should yield bad request with error containing collectionDate
If the collection_date is in future, there should be an error with collection_date invalid
Should throw a bad request if there is no collection method specified
Should throw a bad request if the collection method is invalid
should throw a bad request if data source is not specified
Should throw a bad request if the data source is invalid and not in the list
should throw a bad request if flex-schema is not added
should throw an invalid flex schema error if the flex schema is not in the given list
Should give out success if the valid parameters are sent
